    <briefdescription>
<para>IWDG HAL module driver. This file provides firmware functions to manage the following functionalities of the Independent Watchdog (IWDG) peripheral: </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="author"><para>MCD Application Team<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Initialization and Start functions</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>IO operation functions</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</simplesect>
<simplesect kind="attention"><para></para>
</simplesect>
Copyright (c) 2017 STMicroelectronics. All rights reserved.</para>
